title: #92Noon! Zimm/Miller/Leber/Grimm/Motzko/Panagos
description: Packed show! First hour: Vikings ATopics, Mike Zimmer X's & O's chat, then Lions vox Dan Miller....Second Hour: Leber in studio followed by Gophers voice Mike Grimm...Final hour: Memory Lane with Vikes/Lions, Gopher hockey coach Bob Motzko, then Gopher football DL coach Jim Panagos!
